      <title>Trump says U.S. military fatally struck another alleged drug-smuggling boat</title>
      <author>The Associated Press</author>
      <link>https://www.npr.org/2025/09/20/nx-s1-5547852/trump-military-strike-drug-smuggling-boat</link>
